videos.description: Gonzaga's Zach Norvell Jr. gets the steal, goes all the way for a big dunk and gets fouled.
videos.headline: Norvell Jr. hammers the dunk while getting fouled

videos.description: Josh Perkins throws up the lob and Killian Tillie slams down the alley-oop on the fast break.
videos.headline: Tillie dunks home the pass in transition for Gonzaga

videos.description: Jaylen Nowell passes down low to Carlos Johnson who jams it home for the Huskies.
videos.headline: Johnson slams it home for Washington

videos.description: Unselfish passing by Gonzaga leads to Johnathan Williams finishing down low plus the foul.
videos.headline: Good passing by Gonzaga results in and-1 shot for Williams

videos.description: Josh Perkins lobs it up and Rui Hachimura slams it down for Gonzaga.
videos.headline: Hachimura throws down the pass for the dunk
